#

Chicken Tikka Masala

35 min
$15
500 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

Indian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

IndianComfort FoodQuick Meal

Description

A creamy, spiced chicken dish that’s comforting and full of flavor, perfect for any night.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 lb
  • tikka masala sauce: 1 jar (16 oz)
  • yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • ginger: 1 inch
  • onion: 1 medium
  • cilantro: for garnish
  • rice: 2 cups (cooked)
  • salt: to taste
  • oil: 2 tablespoons
